# Per-deploy wrangler config. Tracked template lives in
# wrangler.toml.example; copy it on first checkout, fill in your own
# values, and keep your real config local-only:
#
#   cp wrangler.toml.example wrangler.toml
wrangler.toml

# Internal-only documentation. Operator runbooks and integration
# specs name the Cloudflare account id, D1 database UUID, and the
# service hostnames specific to this deployment. They have no value
# to public readers / forkers of this fork; keep them local.
docs/ops-*.md
docs/integration-spec.md
